<section class="oe_container">
    <div class="oe_row oe_spaced">
           <h2 class="oe_slogan" style="color:olive;"><b>Job Order / Work Order with Start and Stop Timer and Digital Customer Signature</h2>
           <h3 class="oe_slogan" style="color:green;"><b>Web Application and Responsive on Mobiles/Tablets</h3>
           <p class="oe_mt32" style="color:olive;">
                This app help employees to set Duration By buttons and it will allowed customer to sign on task after completing job order
                
          </p>
          <p style="color:CRIMSON;"><b>
                Main Features:
          </p>

          <p style="color:olive;">
             <li style="color:olive;">Allow your technician or user to start/stop/pause clock timer on job order form of website portal my account page. So your technician can go to customer location start/stop/pause timer based on job order he/she has been assigned and working.</li>
             <li style="color:olive;">Record Timer information on job order form.</li>
             <li style="color:olive;">Durations are store on job order form.</li>
             <li style="color:olive;">Allow your customer to signature on job order. Signature box added on website page of users job order list.</li>
             <li style="color:olive;">Digital signataure will be store in backend job order record.</li>
             <li style="color:olive;">Allow you to do multiple start/stop/pause for same job order.</li>
             <li style="color:olive;">On stop of timer system will automatically pass some of data and open mobile timesheet view where user can directly fill timesheet for his/her work.</li>
             <li style="color:olive;">Mobile / Tablets reponsive. You can also use this as web application on your browser like chrome, firefox etc..</li>
             <li style="color:olive;">Allow your technician to go onsite at customer location and access it on his/her mobile devices.</li>
             <li style="color:olive;">Fully integrated with backend job order app.</li>
             <li style="color:olive;">Note that this is not Android or IOS made application. This is made using core Odoo Web Responsive framework.</li>
             <li style="color:green;">This app is depend on our job order costing sheet app. You can see dependancies. So you will have all features of dependant apps.</li>
             <li style="color:green;">For more details please watch Video.</li>
             <li style="color:green;">Any question you can contact us by email or from Probuse Website.</li>
          </p>
    </div>
</section>

